gmoji\" /><br />\n唔使出手都會經濟攬炒<br />\n我睇佢禁得幾奈<br />\n<br />\n呢排得閒啲未走下資撳下錢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大把文宣野，和理非野可以做"},{"pid":"edd7900c5b2652477c108d54817611f83ff672c4","tid":1642390,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c71d744b7a1f9212dce6ee7962f819383a8bc09b","tid":1642390,"uid":54220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T18:54:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔認同唔拆鐵<br />\n不過拆鐵高風險都係真嘅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T18:58:10.000Z","msg":"一開任即掉兩個魔法火球去個入口度 然後就打其他塔 唔好聚晒係度"},{"pid":"d8095f7e1a610dcaff5f6040ed18c125746ec643","tid":1642390,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T19:48:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f44fd641ef799ff673c6e713f69a6553207b927d","tid":1642390,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T19:55:48.000Z","msg":"搭巴士囉驚閪 大家一齊繼續夜歸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"194992cf9c3f8d15f0274dedd8e49f371cbaa3b4","tid":1642390,"uid":174120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d94a8b9c8edbbffec3907d20dced4cad0c166fc","tid":1642390,"uid":167179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T18:38:58.000Z","msg":"唔好爆港鐵廣告牌，一塊廣告牌賺嘅廣告錢多過你幾千人交通費。<br />\n最賤係你爆廣告位冇阻佢交通運作，冇藉口停冇得搵位入你地。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T20:03:24.000Z","msg":"agree"},{"pid":"360acf20ab4d8bccfee2ca2c784833da311cb550","tid":1642390,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"194992cf9c3f8d15f0274dedd8e49f371cbaa3b4","tid":1642390,"uid":174120,"like